FBIS3-8025 "dreeu042_p_94003" FBIS-EEU-94-042 Document Type:Daily Report 3 Mar 1994 POLAND UOP Refuses Comment on Lysenko Remarks LD0203155194 Warsaw Radio Warszawa Network in Polish 1400 GMT 2 Mar 94 LD0203155194 Warsaw Radio Warszawa Network Language: Polish Article Type:BFN [Text] The State Protection Office [UOP] has refused to comment on statements by Anatoliy Lysenko, a major in the Ukrainian security sevices, accused of spying. During today's trial before a military court, Lysenko said that the UOP had been encouraging him to cooperate and accept Polish citizenship. He added that he had been urged to sign papers he did not understand.
